---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Games" description="Explore games from Quiet Atlas - healing-oriented, contemplative experiences.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="masthead">
        <div class="date">The Quiet Atlas Chronicle</div>
        <h1>Games</h1>
        <p class="text-faded text-serif">Dispatches from the Atlas</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="games-content container">
    <!-- Featured Game: Bullet Well -->
    <article class="game-feature fade-in">
      <div class="game-feature-header">
        <div class="headline-group">
          <span class="edition">First Edition</span>
          <h2 class="headline">
            <span class="headline-small">Local Studio Unveils</span>
            <span class="headline-large">Bullet Well</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="subheadline">
            An Unlikely Marriage of Whimsy and Chaos Captivates Players Worldwide
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="game-feature-body columns-wrapper">
        <div class="game-columns">
          <div class="column">
            <p class="drop-cap">
              In an age of ever-increasing complexity, one small studio has dared to ask: 
              what if chaos could feel like play? The answer, it seems, is Bullet Well—a 
              peculiar arcade experience that defies easy categorization.
            </p>
            <p>
              "We wanted something that felt like discovering a game drawn in the margins 
              of your notebook," explains the development team. "Something with personality, 
              even if that personality is a little unhinged."
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="column">
            <h3>The Mechanics</h3>
            <p>
              At its core, Bullet Well borrows the vertical momentum of the beloved Doodle Jump 
              while introducing the beautiful mathematics of bullet hell. Players ascend through 
              an endless scribble-scape, dodging hand-drawn projectiles that seem to have a mind 
              of their own.
            </p>
            <p>
              The art style—reminiscent of hurried sketches during a particularly boring 
              lecture—gives the chaos a disarming charm. This is not a game that takes itself 
              seriously, and that may be precisely its strength.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <aside class="game-sidebar">
          <div class="info-box">
            <h4>Quick Facts</h4>
            <dl>
              <dt>Genre</dt>
              <dd>Arcade / Bullet Hell</dd>
              <dt>Style</dt>
              <dd>Hand-drawn / Scribble Art</dd>
              <dt>Platform</dt>
              <dd>Available on itch.io</dd>
            </dl>
            <a href="https://quietatlas.itch.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">
              Play Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
      
      <div class="game-feature-footer">
        <div class="pull-quote">
          "A game drawn in the margins of your notebook—with personality to spare."
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Coming Soon Section -->
    <section class="coming-soon fade-in">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span>Coming Soon</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="coming-soon-content content-width text-center">
        <p class="text-large text-serif">
          More dispatches are being prepared.<br/>
          New stories are being drawn.
        </p>
        <p class="text-faded">
          Follow our journey on <a href="https://quietatlas.itch.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">itch.io</a> 
          to be notified when new games emerge from the atlas.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .games-content {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  /* Game Feature Article */
  .game-feature {
    background: var(--paper-aged);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .game-feature::before,
  .game-feature::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    background: var(--paper-aged);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  
  .game-feature::before {
    top: 5px;
    left: 5px;
    right: -5px;
    bottom: -5px;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  
  .game-feature::after {
    top: 10px;
    left: 10px;
    right: -10px;
    bottom: -10px;
    z-index: -2;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  
  .game-feature-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--ink);
  }
  
  .edition {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--ink-faded);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
  }
  
  .headline {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .headline-small {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  
  .headline-large {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  
  .subheadline {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  /* Columns Layout */
  .columns-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .game-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .column h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
  }
  
  .column p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-align: justify;
    hyphens: auto;
  }
  
  /* Sidebar */
  .game-sidebar {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .info-box {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(70px + var(--space-lg));
  }
  
  .info-box h4 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  
  .info-box dl {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .info-box dt {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-faded);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .info-box dd {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-left: 0;
  }
  
  .info-box .btn {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .game-feature-footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .columns-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .game-sidebar {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-faded);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    }
    
    .info-box {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      align-items: end;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    
    .info-box h4 {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    
    .info-box .btn {
      width: auto;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .game-columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .column p {
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .info-box {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  /* Coming Soon */
  .coming-soon {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .coming-soon-content {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .coming-soon-content p {
    max-width: 100%;
  }
</style>
